Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:41.33,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:42.66,Danna ga Nani Main,rino,0,0,0,,Parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:43.54,Danna ga Nani Main,nozomu,0,0,0,,Parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:44.50,Danna ga Nani Main,tanak,0,0,0,,Parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:45.33,Danna ga Nani Main,yama,0,0,0,,Parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:46.37,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,Meus parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:47.33,Danna ga Nani Main,mayo,0,0,0,,Parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.58,Danna ga Nani Main,mom,0,0,0,,Parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:50.59,Danna ga Nani Main,dad,0,0,0,,Parabéns...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.76,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Boatos se espalham muito rápido.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:55.21,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,Não fui eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.09,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Você está nervoso?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.34,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:01.47,Danna ga Nani Main,rino,0,0,0,,O que tiver que ser, será. \N Vocês ficarão bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.35,Danna ga Nani Main,nozomu,0,0,0,,Sim, exatamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:07.60,Danna ga Nani Main,tana,0,0,0,,Estou aqui, não se preocupe. \N Farei tudo o que puder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:08.35,Danna ga Nani Main,yama,0,0,0,,Isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.36,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,Então, como você se sente?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.15,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Não sinto como se fosse real.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:14.86,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Não consigo para de pensar \N se um cara como eu merece isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:18.86,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Como se talvez fosse um sonho e tudo fosse desaparecer amanhã.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:21.37,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,Nada de errado irá acontecer. Não irei deixar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:23.49,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,Não aceitarei esse destino...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.54,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,Irei destruí-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:26.08,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Que manifesto de ódio camarada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.08,Danna ga Nani Main,mayo,0,0,0,,Irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:30.50,Danna ga Nani Main,mayo,0,0,0,,Irei lhe fazer uma pergunta que \N não poderia responder um ano atrás.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.84,Danna ga Nani Main,mayo,0,0,0,,Ei, por que o Pai sempre está em casa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.63,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Porque ele trabalha em casa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:36.71,Danna ga Nani Main,mayo,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.38,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Rock you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.38,Danna ga Nani Main,Nota,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an8\i1}Trad. Literal: “Te detonei!”{\i0}
