Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:42.14,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Estou certo de que o resultado será apenas um mal-entendido novamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.30,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Rápido! Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.81,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Seja paciente...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.27,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Ah, eu não estou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.64,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Bem, ficará por conta dos deuses, afinal de contas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:49.27,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Vê?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.94,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Ah, que pen— Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:55.78,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:08.41,Danna ga Nani Main I,haji,0,0,0,,Na realidade, a vida cotidiana não acaba tão dramaticamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:12.71,Danna ga Nani Main I,haji,0,0,0,,Vai junto ao silêncio, às vezes supera os limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.46,Danna ga Nani Main I,haji,0,0,0,,com uma mistura de felicidade e preocupação...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.97,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Licença maternidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.97,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sankyuu (産休)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:21.01,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:21.01,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Obrigada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.64,Danna ga Nani Main I,haji,0,0,0,,Em tempos tranquilos e em tempos ocupados,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:27.18,Danna ga Nani Main I,haji,0,0,0,,viver de modo banal continua sendo andar para frente, \N para nunca voltar para trás.
